---
export const prerender = false;

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Photographs, writing, and experiments in AI.">
  <p>
    In the Summer of 2025, I was hospitalized for approaching perfection.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site is where I share photographs, writing, and experiments in AI.
  </p>
  <p>
    All photographs are actually for free. I will mail you one. Just give me your
    mailing address via the <a href="/contact">contact form</a>, and I will mail you a photo.
  </p>
  <blockquote class="about-quote">
    <p>&ldquo;Practice any art&hellip; not to get money and fame, but to make your soul grow.&rdquo;</p>
    <cite>&mdash; Kurt Vonnegut</cite>
  </blockquote>
  <p class="meta">
    Matthew R. Kenney, Bloomfield, New Jersey, father of three, owner of two dogs with PTSD.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-quote {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  .about-quote p {
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .about-quote cite {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
</style>
